    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >远古世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切始于公元前一万年。你将带领人类走过一段漫长而艰辛的发展之路——从旧石器时代起步，最终迈入铁器时代。游戏中设有庞大的科技树，随着技术不断解锁，你的玩法也将随之演变，使你可以灵活应对全新的挑战。与此同时，你的聚落将逐渐壮大，不仅规模扩张，其科技水平也日益精进。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/f891e6c14991300650a78fba599a561f.poster.avif?t=1770138259\" width=780 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/f891e6c14991300650a78fba599a561f.webm?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/f891e6c14991300650a78fba599a561f.mp4?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定居者的日常</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要建造房屋、采集资源、制作工具、开垦农田、驯养牲畜，还要熔炼青铜与铁器。游戏初期资源极其有限，因此头几年的首要任务就是——活下去！毕竟，定居者要先能吃饱穿暖，才能谈发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/73e7e96d1fd7f4d9c7240d995c295289.poster.avif?t=1770138259\" width=780 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/73e7e96d1fd7f4d9c7240d995c295289.webm?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/73e7e96d1fd7f4d9c7240d995c295289.mp4?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >回合制玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  游戏以“天”为单位推进，每一天都是一个完整的行动回合。在每个回合中，定居者只能完成有限的工作量，因此如何高效分配任务、最大化产出，就成了你的核心课题。就像我们都熟悉的那句：“再来一回合！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/21d1f16168f672ffa5f420810e810fdc.poster.avif?t=1770138259\" width=780 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/21d1f16168f672ffa5f420810e810fdc.webm?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/21d1f16168f672ffa5f420810e810fdc.mp4?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 世界地图</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将探索一个六边形构成的回合制世界地图。探索途中，你会发现各种珍贵资源：新的作物种子、可驯化的动物，还有更多奇妙事件，等待你一一发掘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/e059f5fb69c9e41e611294dabab6df65.poster.avif?t=1770138259\" width=780 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/e059f5fb69c9e41e611294dabab6df65.webm?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/e059f5fb69c9e41e611294dabab6df65.mp4?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建筑与地形</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用独特的建筑网格系统——由随机生成的不规则四边形拼接而成。地形则由大型方块组成，完全可自由编辑。想开沟填海，还是堆山造丘？都没问题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/240e136322dc9b7e1ffcd49a3540cd6e.poster.avif?t=1770138259\" width=780 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/240e136322dc9b7e1ffcd49a3540cd6e.webm?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/240e136322dc9b7e1ffcd49a3540cd6e.mp4?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >聚落防御</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >荒野中的猛兽与敌对的游牧部落不会坐视你发展壮大。务必武装你的定居者，修筑带有塔楼的城墙，守护来之不易的家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/102887362112f00b666d95080a502165.poster.avif?t=1770138259\" width=780 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/102887362112f00b666d95080a502165.webm?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112740/extras/102887362112f00b666d95080a502165.mp4?t=1770138259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >其他亮点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序化生成的世界：每次开局，地貌都会随机生成。游戏开始前，你可以按喜好预选理想的貌形类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >法律与年度计划系统：通过制定律法和年度目标，你可以深度定制自己的发展路线。部分年度计划会随机触发，为游戏注入轻度Roguelike元素，让每局体验都充满变数。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工具决定效率：工欲善其事，必先利其器。快去打造铁斧、铁镐和青铜斧这些高效装备吧！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏由一位开发者倾注热爱独自完成。愿你在 Humanica 的世界里，感受到那份对文明演进的敬意与乐趣！</p>",
